      "imagery": "Imagery primarily consists of high-quality product photography and architectural renders. These visuals are typically contained within their sections, often shown as part of a larger composition or in a grid, with clean edges. Product shots are often full-frame or tightly cropped, emphasizing the material and form of the furniture. There are minimal decorative illustrations or abstract graphics. Icons are monochrome, typically filled where present, and serve a functional purpose.",
